data.description: Welcome to your new home!  This hidden gem boasts three bedrooms and two baths, modern comfort and an array of desirable features.  The home has an appointed master bedroom and an updated interior with stylish finishes and a fresh, contemporary look.  The laundry is located within the home for convenience and the floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas.  Enjoy extra security and privacy with a gated front yard and fenced in backyard.  Step outside to a spacious covered patio area, perfect for outdoor dining, hosting gatherings, and an expansive backyard that is a blank canvas for your landscaping dreams.  Don't miss this great opportunity to make it your forever home!
